Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请容我讲解GUNDAM FIGHT的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那起源自60年前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开被极度污染的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞上宇宙的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了避免卫星国家之间爆发全面战争
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.63,0:01:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是创立每四年一度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各国派出代表的Fighter操纵名为GUNDAM的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以FIGHT的方式不断战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后胜出的GUNDAM代表的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能得到卫星国家联邦的主导权
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然创出充满体育精神的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，剩下的问题有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这项FIGHT的舞台是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，就是我们居住的被极度污染的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，今届大赛看来有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的人，你有见过这男人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这照片会掀起多猛烈的战斗风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的对手是neo Russia的代表Bolt Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听闻Fighter是个Prisoner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}大逃亡！被囚禁的Gundam Fighter！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，不知从什么时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:03:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一带称为GUNDAM坟场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入市内的GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会消失得无影无踪，不会再出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没讲过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般游客不会有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这种有监狱的市镇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，多蒙的确来了这市镇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM坟场？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？他们为何在找GUNDAM？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲！你的真正身份是Gundam Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里是找neo Russia的Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…讲过很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一般的游客啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还狡辩！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快讲出你的GUNDAM在哪里！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙只是在市内四处游荡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，听闻他在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠那些证据也不可证明他是Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我们的情报网是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人一定是neo Japan的Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些国家名是什么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，告诉我，这男人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我解开手铐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赶快替他治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的手便会废掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这照片我收回了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样便行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？那班人有何目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:05:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人…即使怎样挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能逃离这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大块头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像同样是囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可惜我不能在这种地方浪费时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨碍我的统统给我滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的拳劲…无效！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事要问那男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，我也要你规矩一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁哥·加鲁斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，即使不能插手外国的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我们也…拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，我再多观察一会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙那家伙，总是要我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宁愿跟他绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙…多蒙·卡休
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？那怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点捉住他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后，把那部Devil Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，只有那方法才可救到他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你才能救他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看来做了很可怕的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你还是彻底死心比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一被关进这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生便完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Fighter先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你隐瞒，我巴杜文大爷也知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每四年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会有你这类人被关进这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，他们会都跌进陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那班人发放消息说neo Russia的GUNDAM在那市镇里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把每一个来到的敌国的Fighter捉住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关进这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，neo Russia便不战而胜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被隔离在这个任何通讯方法也无效的岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外国的人便无法插手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和外界永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你估计被囚的Fighter会有何下场？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们要在这里拼命工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群被囚的丧家犬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，不可以轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Fighter变成这样便完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Russia的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用这种方法收集各国的最新科技用来制造GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该很强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定会成功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派我们的Fighter混入囚犯里做间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后令他说出GUNDAM藏在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得真周到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，从另一角度看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是天堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，在大赛中失踪的Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是国家的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这里后也只会被追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是，你也是其中一个Fighter？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别胡说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一般罪犯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外你还是快点说出GUNDAM的所在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！那家伙做什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们做什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，站在那里不要动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好，放我出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着，明天工作结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来我身边，一起离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守卫比想像中更加深严
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不能查明多蒙是否在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海上又不能把核战车交给他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你也不知死活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去，你会没命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点说出GUNDAM的所在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外，你想离开这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为多谢你照顾我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎样逃走？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你能偷一部车回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一出去便会掉进海里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行不通啊，行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点放弃你的GUNDAM吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚好冷啊，好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？那男人有所行动？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，只靠那点情报
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不知他何时会逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起的间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人在打什么主意？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？你走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和这些雀鸟分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲，你想怎样逃走？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要令这些…能源管爆炸！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救火！快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警卫队！囚犯逃狱呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样冲出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但正面不行啊！怎办？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结冰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日的寒冷天气令湖结冰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了！我自由了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自由了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙的反应恢复了，好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙竟然逃走！他有何打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bolt Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，由我这里远程控制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差少许便能去到市镇了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，看来不能轻易到达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，它来得太快了，难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！我没通风报讯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先阻止他们前进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那家伙是间谍吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:15:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上来！是核战车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你，莉茵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧！Shining Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是neo Japan的Shining Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来阿鲁哥想和这家伙决斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假装逃狱引敌人的GUNDAM出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好，剩下的交给我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让任何人妨碍我战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM FIGHT，准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…GUNDAM FIGHT！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星鎚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，我一起向你和那铁球报恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好机会！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击中！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的头竟能承受多蒙的拳劲！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看neo Russia的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁哥，毁掉它的头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么？这就完了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监狱里那场架只是虚有其表吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也只有这点技俩吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的头是我的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！年轻人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这只手在闪耀和咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在叫我打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，是打和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错…我不能战斗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人，阿鲁哥·加鲁斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你的拳里感到监狱的囚犯所没有的Fighter灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是想跟你决斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他因此而逃狱？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:20:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以前是个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处抢掠卫星的宇宙海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听闻他参加今届大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了换取同伴的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装在他胸膛的炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换言之他永远是个囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一剩下的自由只有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我不认识这男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今后有何打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看过你们刚才的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也记起我是个放弃了自由的Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会继续逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至再次得到自由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，别忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM FIGHT国际条约第七条
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球是擂台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们身为Fighter的一日在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也和他一样是囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，我也是囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.31,0:22:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个名为地球的擂台的囚犯

Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:32.04,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便数千的日夜流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:36.43,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:40.87,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨着 追求着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:44.44,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫步着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.68,0:22:51.59,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋人啊 在我瞳孔的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:22:57.29,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实摇曳着的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:23:02.60,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何传达才好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:09.08,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让受伤的心与身体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:13.26,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这温暖的怀抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:19.25,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比海更深沉的睡去吧

Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.38,0:23:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遣送回neo Japan殖民卫星的多蒙\N等待他的是可怕的测试
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片上的男人究竟是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为最强最恶的Devil Gundam又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.58,0:23:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙真正的目的现在水落石出了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.39,0:23:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 机动武斗传G GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.75,0:23:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗吧多蒙！地球就是擂台！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.02,0:23:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！


